          "The purpose of these GTC is to define the general conditions under which ATB Technologies SAS, as a technical and contractual intermediary, makes the ATB AgriTrace Platform available to Buyers and Sellers — a digital marketplace enabling the connection, negotiation, traceability, EUDR compliance certification, and transaction security for agricultural products originating from West Africa. ATB acts as an agent within the meaning of Article 98 of the OHADA Uniform Act on General Commercial Law, and not as buyer or seller of the Products, unless expressly stipulated otherwise in a separate contract.",
